{"tid":1516493,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"好慘 今朝開記招個幾個小朋友比人當condom","createTime":"2019-08-29T14:47:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T16:16:30.000Z","uid":274079,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"40c9e058c80c10b168415b08c40697fa43912c6c","tid":1516493,"uid":274079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:47:32.000Z","msg":"(代朋友po)<br />\n<br />\n相信大家都知道今朝中學生罷課聯盟(由多個細gp組合而成既中學生罷課大gp)開左個記招，但開完記招之後聯盟高層(gp owner加小部份admin)當晒我地係condom，為左之後不被抹黑，我地決定發出以下聲明。<br />\n<br />\n首先，一開始有呢個gp既時候(大約一個月前)，大家分工透明度都好高，大家會互相報告自己既工作進度，但由26.8之後，gp owner同佢地既&ldquo;高層&rdquo;開始冇左一直以來既透明度，我地完全唔知佢地個邊既進度去到邊，而我地亦一直有匯報我地既進度，亦清楚講明今日會開press con而當時係冇任何人反對，仲有幫手搵場地！<br />\n<br />\n但高層們係我地開完press con之後竟然話我地自把自為，要解散中聯罷聯盟，所以我地決定會重開一個新既組織，並繼續組織罷課既工作。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W2m3bDh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW2m3bDh.png&h=5fd7f84c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V4CxPpY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV4CxPpY.png&h=30e8c092&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qCct7bD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqCct7bD.jpg&h=66c37873&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KkgKFwE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKkgKFwE.jpg&h=7dbd1367&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nFL3V40.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnFL3V40.jpg&h=c96bc3c7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fXJX0wG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfXJX0wG.jpg&h=b568107b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dbr6TRG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdbr6TRG.jpg&h=69cdc1fd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TnQLpYn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTnQLpYn.jpg&h=09597bc7&s